bles: [p110_devices, unterverteilung_devices])\r\n  |\u003e pivot(rowKey:[\"_time\"], columnKey:[\"_measurement\"], valueColumn: \"_value\")\r\n  |\u003e drop(columns: [\"_start\", \"_stop\", \"_field\"])",
